enb_long_title: Tenth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
sentences: Organization of the intergovernmental process: An SBI in-session workshop on the organization of the intergovernmental process was held on Saturday, 11 December.

Participants heard panel statements and considered the content, timing and adoption of the agendas of the COP, SBSTA and SBI, and the 'building blocks' of the process, including COP and SB sessions, workshops and constituted bodies.
A summary of the in-session workshop is available at: http://www.iisd.ca/vol12/enb12255e.html
